name: onedev
description: Self-hosted Git Server with CI/CD and Kanban

commit.message: Fix issue #861 - Retry all failed/cancelled builds
Fix issue #880 - Boards: Allow "No Milestone" in milestone dropdown
Update backlog description

Fix issue #882 - Issues List: Doesn't use first saved query when OneDev
redirects to issues list
Bump version to 7.4.22
Remove service desk marker line as this is not necessary.
Minor css fix
Fix issue #863 - Unexpected cancellation of build jobs
Fix issue #878 - Able to specify line numbers only when referencing source lines

Fix issue #874 - CodeIndexer exception - Indexing large repo with Lucene
results in exception.

Fix issue #871 - [service desk] Add option to trim replies send out by
1dev
Bump version

Performance improvements and bugfixes

Fix issue #876 - Unauthorized users watching issue still gets notified after an issue is marked as confidential
Fix issue #875 - Performance improvements for large number of users
Bump version to 7.4.20
Fix issue #859 - [Helpdesk] Can't add (required) issue creation settings
Fix issue #867 - A button to copy error detail when exception occurs

Fix issue #856 - Automatic escaping of characters in secret during git
sync

Fix issue #858 - Validate system email address to make sure it is
well-formed in mail setting
Fix issue #857 - Table border in markdown is not displayed
Add more trace logs for mail inbox handling

Fix issue #855 - Record commit in OneDev package and use this info to
decide whether or not to upgrade
Fix issue #854 - default branch via api
Bump version to 7.4.18

More robust logic to remove quoted content when creating comment from
mail message
Add more mail checking log
Fix issue #839 - Large comments trimmed
#850 - Unable to post issue comment if stay on the page for some time
Remove warnings
Fix issue #847 - Unable to parse some unit test report from Go/Jest report
fixed IDE issue, enabled second test
